    },
    {
        src: ServiceImg2,
        alt: "Business & corporate law",
        title: "Migration Matters",
        description:
            "Our migration legal practitioners perform compliance check and pre-assessment for you, that you will know your strength and weakness before your application is submitted. We also have 13+ years of experience in migration appeals",
    },
    {
        src: ServiceImg7,
        alt: "Criminal defense",
        title: "Commercial Matters",
        description:
            "The best approach to tackle commercial disputes domestic or international is having the strongest commercial risk solutions which we can do with our extensive commercial litigation experience..",
    },
    {
